{"tid":2121312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(BNO) 點解香港人會覺得6年係\"捱\"同\"嫌長\"?","createTime":"2020-07-23T08:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T15:07:01.000Z","uid":84147,"like":68,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0f23e1a764e400addb7370e39a8bc2a095ed25a5","tid":2121312,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:32:09.000Z","msg":"香港人一聽到6年就嫌長<br />\n我真係r撚哂頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通限住你住得短反而係件好事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係住3年同住6年，你會簡住3年即刻番港共捱？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">即係過左6年你就即刻拎英國護照番香港？係香港就變左唔係捱而係享受？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係佢天日將6年變做2年，你就只係住2年再即刻番香港買番納米樓住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><ins><strong>仲有，點解用係用捱依個字而唔係用享受依2個字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係你潛意識覺得去英國係降左grade？</strong></ins></span>香港生活好撚過英國你先會覺得住6年係捱唔係生活？<br />\n<br />\n如果你係攬抄派知道香港無得救，咁佢改做6年同10年有咩分別？唔通改短左對你有著數？佢比你住得愈耐唔係愈好咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><ins><strong>佢改6年，係保障你可以享受至少6年自由生活，6年內佢人口點膨脹都趕唔到你番港共捱，而唔洗好似其他難民咁住1，2年咩都未定就比人掟番香港</strong></ins>，愈長愈著數，只要你係想逃離香港，<strong><span class=\"x-large\">你幾時拎到本護照有咩所謂？唔通你拎完護照就即刻番香港享受人生？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"86ab57efc4af0d325f5ab909a18ab688a73f20fc","tid":2121312,"uid":90328,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:33:11.000Z","msg":"香港人做慣狗係咁"},{"pid":"c384ecdd694ce72582947958b367c5ae34a504b6","tid":2121312,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"