uired, it may be retained despite absences from the UK of up to 2 years but may be forfeited if absences are longer without good reason.<br />\n<br />\n鬆到咁，仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}